quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  100,1,"And/by the panting/changing colour , attacking forces/horses"
  100,2,"So the igniters (of fire)/swayers , fire striking/sparking/decaying"
  100,3,So the raiders/fast attacking horses (in) mornings/daybreaks
  100,4,So they stirred and arose/agitated dust/splashing mud or water with it
  100,5,So they were in the middle with it all together/(in) a group
  100,6,That truly the human/mankind (is) ungrateful/disobedient (E) to his Lord
  100,7,And he truly (is) on that witnessing/testifying (E)
  100,8,And that he truly to the good`s/wealth`s love/like (is) strong (intense) (E) (humans love excessive goodness)
  100,9,So does he not know when what (is) in the graves/burial places is scattered/over thrown/strewn
  100,10,And what (is) in the chests (innermosts) is recovered/collected
  100,11,That truly their Lord (is) with them (on) that day expert/experienced (E)